			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1933138">
									

<p>So, going by the logic of this, if the creator of the anomaly was a demi-deity adult male&#8230; it would be &quot;Spiral Blackman&quot;? Or &quot;Spiral Blackadult&quot;, which just sounds ridiculous?</p>
